divs: Sighting DetailsI am reporting this for a co-worker. He was driving on Rt. 128 about 4 PM when he saw what looked like a rocket going straight up into the sky leaving a single contrail. He commented that it didn't look like a plane's contrail; it was single and going straight up into the sky. Since I am a member of Mufon he asked me to see if anyone else reported seeing anything on the Monday Sept 21st.
trends: There have been 2 other sightings in Newton
There were no other sightings in Newton on or around September 21st 2009
Summary: Missle like object seen leaving a contrail going straight up.
